<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Export Control Joint Unit (ECJU) administers the UK’s system of export controls and licensing for military and dual-use items. ECJU is part of the Department for Business and Trade ."@en .
